724
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,510
Is that possible?

725
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,440
I see you're well-informed.

726
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,750
The best private room at Dukang Restaurant

727
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:39,880
