no need to wait for all guests to arrive.

737
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,480
Serve the food promptly at 3 pm

738
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,900
with plenty of good wine.

739
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:57,480
Alright.

