754
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:19,880
in detail.

755
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:21,690
The more specific, the better.

756
00:32:22,250 --> 00:32:22,830
Let's go.

757
00:32:29,110 --> 00:32:29,640
Sir.

